summary: You’re Reading Manhua The Strongest Body Refiner in History Full Raw Updated At Manhua Website The Strongest Body Refiner in History English Translated The body refined by a hundred thousand demons, the skin tempered by the flesh and blood of ten thousand devils, the veins as clear as heavenly YinYang light, the soul formed by the stars of a multitude of worlds~ Ye CangXuan is the foremost body refiner in the world. So, in this era Ye CangXuan becomes a mortal to experience many difficulties and restore his divinity, left to rely on his unparalleled body refining skills.
